{"tid":2387341,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"訂閱者破三百萬！韓國藝人斜槓Youtuber最強TOP 5，Jennie一天就直接破百萬！","createTime":"2021-01-30T08:53:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T11:27:47.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cdbdcd461ba551589c3b38e58e42e111eb3e83a9","tid":2387341,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T08:53:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_2cc9974ce7f03b4f071a56849eac38f0/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-29/133346-895178.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_2cc9974ce7f03b4f071a56849eac38f0%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-29%2F133346-895178.jpg&h=b4162b46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現在也越來越多藝人會利用Youtube這個平台，跟粉絲互動，一起分享私底下的樣子呢～"},{"pid":"a8a6e6eb53ba716a3dc35490296f60a565153a8b","tid":2387341,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T08:53:22.000Z","msg":"TOP.5）EXO 伯賢<br />\n首先是伯賢的個人頻道「백현 Baekhyun」，訂閱數328萬獲得第五位，平常很喜歡分享私底下的日常生活，無論是工作或是寵物方面，都展現出了不一樣的魅力，海外粉絲也是非常的喜歡。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_8a019ceeebcfe0c768651484f91b5d00/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-29/133346-895179.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_8a019ceeebcfe0c768651484f91b5d00%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-29%2F133346-895179.jpg&h=d65ebe9c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d1bea65e29b32c007d730fad0dd0cade578a025","tid":2387341,"uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T08:53:49.000Z","msg":"TOP.4）白種元<br />\n在韓國無人不知的廚師之神白種元，不只會在節目上教學做菜的秘訣，更會在頻道上分享老少咸宜又簡單的食譜，而2018年才開設的頻道也已經擁有478萬的訂閱數呢！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wM9hbmwCpdc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwM9hbmwCpdc&d=auZED%2BZQxHi6416lNwsUjNagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=c42180b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wM9hbmwCpdc</a><br />\n<br />\nTOP.3）Blackpink Jennie<br />\n接著就是在生日當天才開通的「Jennierubyjane Official」，馬上到現在就已經突破491萬，除了破紀錄不到一天就破百萬，目前也只有一支影片，依然話題十足。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_7d06ed5ce989636623334409a452e9e8/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-29/133346-895180.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_7d06ed5ce989636623334409a452e9e8%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-29%2F133346-895180.jpg&h=56313fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=erYPvNbc_mc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DerYPvNbc_mc&d=auZED%2BZQxHi6416lNwsUjNagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=bc5bc8dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=erYPvNbc_mc</a>"},{"pid":"96375e62889251ce4d2b3bbfc601aa5ffae5a945","tid":2387341,"uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T08:54:41.000Z","msg":"TOP.2）Blackpink Lisa<br />\n另外則是同團的Lisa，兩年前開始營運的頻道，也都會分享一些生活VLOG，或是舞蹈表演的影片，平均的觀看率更是非常的高，再次展現了Blackpink的超高人氣！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=By61X4Ku9JE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBy61X4Ku9JE&d=auZED%2BZQxHi6416lNwsUjNagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=6872cea8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=By61X4Ku9JE</a><br />\n<br />\nTOP.1）IU<br />\n第一名則是由IU「이지금 [IU Official]」的521萬拿下，其中的小單元IU的調色板，更是每每能獲得超高的點閱率，超高質量的節目內容，不只能展現自身的歌聲魅力，還能跟粉絲一起互動。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_4eaa847715523bffb24c70b4d6d417c9/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-29/133346-895181.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_4eaa847715523bffb24c70b4d6d417c9%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-29%2F133346-895181.jpg&h=41552e74&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c7178da986bc0efd1917ff99a601d426673e9d8","tid":2387341,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"